<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GLOBAL TENDENCE FESTIVAL</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0B0B0C;
            --text-color: #E4E4E7;
            --accent-gold: #FFD700;
            --neon-cyan: #00F0FF;
            --neon-green: #39FF14;
            --card-bg: #141416;
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 19px; 
        }
        .container { max-width: 930px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
        
        .video-box {
            width: 100%;
            height: 480px;
            background: #000;
            margin: 35px 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 2px solid #222;
        }
        .video-box iframe { width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; }

        .tag-top { font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 4px; color: #A1A1AA; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: bold; }
        .sub-manifesto { color: var(--neon-green); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 3px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 5px; display: block; }
        .sub-cardine { color: var(--neon-cyan); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 3px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 5px; display: block; }
        
        h1 { font-size: 56px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #FFF; line-height: 1.1; }
        h2 { font-size: 38px; color: #FFF; margin-bottom: 25px; font-weight: 800; border-left: 4px solid var(--neon-cyan); padding-left: 15px; margin-top: 45px; }
        h3 { font-size: 24px; color: #FFF; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 700; }
        h4 { font-size: 18px; color: var(--accent-gold); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        
        p { margin-bottom: 25px; color: #D4D4D8; }
        ul { margin-left: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #A1A1AA; }
        li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
        
        .gold-highlight { color: var(--accent-gold); font-weight: 800; }
        .cyan-highlight { color: var(--neon-cyan); font-weight: 700; }
        .green-highlight { color: var(--neon-green); font-weight: 800; }
        .white-highlight { color: #FFF; font-weight: 700; }
        .salerno-faro { color: var(--accent-gold); font-weight: 900; text-decoration: underline; }
        
        blockquote {
            border-left: 4px solid var(--neon-cyan);
            padding: 20px 25px;
            margin: 35px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #F4F4F5;
            background: #111113;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .divider { border-bottom: 2px solid #222; margin: 50px 0; }
        .stacco { margin-top: 30px; }

        .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 25px; margin: 35px 0; }
        .card-neon { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--neon-cyan); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,240,255,0.05); }
        .card-neon h3 { color: var(--neon-cyan); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 22px; }

        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 15px; border: none; text-align: center; }
        .btn-cyan { background: var(--neon-cyan); color: #000; }
        .btn-outline { border: 2px solid var(--neon-cyan); color: var(--neon-cyan); margin-left: 15px; background: transparent; }

        .gtf-box-final {
            background: #16161A;
            border: 1px dashed var(--accent-gold);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .gtf-box-final p {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            font-size: 23px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* STRUTTURE COMPLEMENTARI */
        .city-module {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid #27272A;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .reward-vertical-stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 25px; margin: 40px 0; }
        .reward-rectangle { 
            background: var(--card-bg); 
            border: 1px solid #27272A; 
            padding: 35px; 
            border-radius: 12px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .reward-price { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 900; color: #FFF; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .reward-rectangle.featured { 
            border: 2px solid var(--neon-cyan); 
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .reward-rectangle.isolated-gold { 
            border: 2px solid var(--accent-gold); 
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .btn-paypal { display: block; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; background: #FFF; color: #000; font-weight: bold; border: none; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; text-align: center; margin-top: 15px; }
        .btn-gold { display: block; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; background: var(--accent-gold); color: #000; font-weight: bold; border: none; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; text-align: center; margin-top: 15px; }
        .macro-fund { 
            background: #16161A; 
            border: 2px dashed var(--accent-gold); 
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.15);
            padding: 40px; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            margin: 50px 0; 
        }
        footer { margin-top: 60px; border-top: 1px solid #222; padding-top: 40px; font-size: 16px; color: #A1A1AA; }
        footer p { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.6; }
        
        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #333;
            padding-top: 25px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .footer-grid-item { color: #A1A1AA; line-height: 1.5; }
        .footer-grid-item strong { color: #FFF; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

    <!-- VIDEO 1: LOOP OPENING -->
    <div class="video-box">
        <iframe src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1m2wpvNY69kyojhuOgO4n9aU8K1biW-mR/preview" allow="autoplay"></iframe>
    </div>

    <div class="tag-top">GLOBAL TREND FORUM®</div>
    <h1>HUMAN AT THE CENTER</h1>
    
    <p><strong>Global Trend Forum®</strong> — The geopolitical and cultural Think Tank created to govern the exponential growth of digital technology. This portal is the official voice of the Global Trend Forum®. From here, an <span class="gold-highlight">international ethical vanguard</span> takes root: a vision that places <span class="white-highlight">human talent</span>, <span class="white-highlight">freedom of expression</span>, and the <span class="white-highlight">value of the individual</span> at the absolute center of technological progress.</p>
    
    <a href="#form-delibera" class="btn btn-cyan">Join the Movement</a>
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline">Read the Manifesto</a>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <!-- ETHICAL MANIFESTO SUBTITLE -->
    <span class="sub-manifesto">Ethical Manifesto</span>
    <h2>THE VISION</h2>
    <blockquote>
        "Artificial Intelligence was not created to replace the individual, but as a technological accelerator to <strong>amplify human talent</strong> and freedom of expression. In this epochal transition, <span class="salerno-faro">SALERNO consecrates itself as the capital and global hub</span> of a new Integral Human Evolution, where technology is entirely at the service of Humanity."
    </blockquote>

    <!-- VIDEO 2: VISUAL MANIFESTO -->
    <div class="video-box">
        <iframe src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qZPb1C-iACH6zHJE63XETbzzQaN7i2in/preview"></iframe>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>AMPLIFICATION AND TYPE 1 CIVILIZATION</h2>
    <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card-neon">
            <h3>Amplify, Do Not Replace</h3>
            <p>"Technology at the service of human talent: every tool empowers the person, it does not substitute them."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-neon">
            <h3>Freedom of Expression</h3>
            <p>"We support the voice of the individual as an absolute value to be expanded in the era of automation."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-neon">
            <h3>Salerno Ethical Capital</h3>
            <p>"An international hub where human evolution applied to AI becomes culture, method, and scientific action."</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <blockquote style="border-left-color: var(--accent-gold); background: #141310;">
        <span class="gold-highlight">"Technology serves to elevate Humanity: it exalts authentic individuality above all conflict, releasing its full potential and projecting it toward a Type 1 civilization."</span>
    </blockquote>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>THE MANDATE – THE THREE CORE PILLARS</h2>
    
    <h3>Pillar I — The Evolutionary Heart — The Integral Human</h3>
    <p>"End of the era of technological fear. We use AI as a mirror and empowerment of the individual, the center of gravity of the system. <span class="cyan-highlight">TECHNOLOGY AS AN EXTENSION</span>"</p>

    <h3>Pillar II — The Diplomacy of Convergence — The Geopolitics of Blocks</h3>
    <p>"<span class="salerno-faro">SALERNO</span> is the only Neutral Ground in the world where the <span class="white-highlight">G7, BRICS, and beyond</span> converge not to negotiate conflicts, but to define a Type 1 Civilization. <span class="cyan-highlight">CONVERGENCE WITHOUT CONFLICT</span>"</p>

    <h3>Pillar III — The Non-Dual Synthesis — Universal Algorithmic Ethics</h3>
    <p>"Technology needs a soul. An unshakeable moral bridge that integrates the algorithmic ethics of the Pope with the holistic vision of Buddhism and global traditions. <span class="cyan-highlight">UNIVERSAL ETHICS</span>"</p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <!-- CORE PRINCIPLE SUBTITLE -->
    <span class="sub-cardine">The Core Principle</span>
    <h2>THE ARCHITECTURE OF INTERSECTION</h2>
    <p>The flows of major global visions and international trends (Macro) intersect with the vital energy, authenticity, and cultural action of local communities (Micro). In this scenario, <span class="salerno-faro">SALERNO configures itself as the first Model-City and global catalyst: the “Switzerland of convergences”</span>, the world's first laboratory for the humanization and democratization of Artificial Intelligence, conceived as a planetary blossoming and a strategic accelerator for the transition toward a <span class="gold-highlight">Type 1 Civilization</span>.</p>

    <p><strong>Vertical Synthesis (Macro):</strong> The direct connection between global currents of thought and the real economy of territories. The Forum becomes an ecosystem of total cross-pollination and the universal contact point where scientific vanguards, enlightened thinkers, industrial representatives, and major world faiths (from the West to Buddhism) of the <span class="gold-highlight">G7 and BRICS countries</span> converge beyond any dualistic logic. A pure space, focused on science, philosophy, and overcoming conflicts to write a shared source code.</p>
    
    <p><strong>Circular Flow (Micro):</strong> The standards of technological innovation and knowledge land on the ground through total interaction, transforming the territory of SALERNO into the first incubator of the New Humanism. Simultaneously, the participatory drive and authenticity of citizens ascend upward, redefining global trends and <span class="green-highlight">transforming the supporter into a co-creator of the future.</span></p>

    <!-- GOLD HIGH-IMPACT BOX -->
    <div class="gtf-box-final">
        <p>"Global Trend Forum®: A platform for an international ethical vanguard: talents, communities, and visions converge in an ecosystem of cultural action."</p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <!-- INDUSTRIAL FRAMEWORK -->
    <h2>THE INDUSTRIAL FRAMEWORK – THE THREE OPERATIVE CITIES</h2>
    <p style="font-style: italic; color: #FFF;">SALERNO transforms into a three-dimensional ecosystem where ethics, experience, and scientific observation converge.</p>
    
    <div class="city-module">
        <p><strong>1. CITY 01 · HEADQUARTERS — The Founding City:</strong> "The headquarters, the source code of the ethical framework, where the Popular Resolution for Ethical AI is born and geopolitical protocols are signed. Ethical protocols | Popular Resolution | Global governance"</p>
    </div>

    <div class="city-module">
        <p><strong>2. CITY 02 · TERRITORIAL HARDWARE — The Experiencing City:</strong> "The three-dimensional space where the languages of art, culture, and innovation converge on the ground, transforming the urban context of SALERNO into a living laboratory of ethical and conscious interaction."</p>
    </div>

    <div class="city-module">
        <p><strong>3. CITY 03 · OBSERVATORY — The Observing City:</strong> "The scientific, technological, and philosophical radar of the Forum. A conceptual station connected directly to the <strong>Space Frontier and latest-generation evolutionary AI systems</strong>. Here, global technological advancement is analyzed, and the course of human evolution toward the outside is plotted, harmonizing the grand visions of multiplanetary civilization with terrestrial algorithmic ethics. Space Frontier & Multiplanetary Civilization | Latest-Gen Evolutionary AI | Terrestrial Algorithmic Ethics"</p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>PHYSICAL METAVERSE & GOVERNANCE</h2>
    <p>"A Physical Metaverse where advanced scientific research, culture, and major brands merge to produce the source code of future trends. <span class="cyan-highlight">The entire city of SALERNO becomes the interface and beacon of the new humanism.</span>"</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #A1A1AA;">
        <li>Model of Ethical Governance for AI.</li>
        <li>Systems Integration and Interoperability.</li>
        <li>Data Security and Privacy (Data Sovereignty).</li>
        <li>Development of Value Ecosystems (Long-term impact).</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>GLOBAL TENDENCE FESTIVAL® – ZERO EDITION 2030</h2>
    <p><strong>GLOBAL TENDENCE FESTIVAL (The Soul):</strong> "The Festival and the Exhibition set themselves up as the two performing engines and central implementation tools of the framework. Not two separate elements, but a single major infrastructure capable of generating and putting into practice new market paradigms. Through the convergence of culture, the real economy, and innovation, they become the concrete vehicle for the transition toward a New Humanism and the strategic acceleration toward a <strong>TYPE 1 CIVILIZATION</strong>."</p>
    
    <p><strong>International Exhibition (The Lung):</strong> "The commercial and brand identity space for businesses and institutions. The place where innovation and business meet to build the future of the ethical economy."</p>

    <p><strong>The Districts of SALERNO:</strong> "Territorial mobilization for the Popular Resolution for Ethical AI and the Protection of Local Commerce."</p>
    
    <div class="stacco"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #FFF;">"The local commercial fabric does not just endure the festival, it executes it."</p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>INTEGRATIVE CROWDFUNDING & THE VALUE OF AUTHENTICITY</h2>
    <p>"This economic mobilization campaign represents a parallel function of democratic participation. The funding is integrative with respect to the industrial activities and developments already underway offline by the Global Trend Forum®. It serves to validate the ethical vision and the Popular Resolution, guaranteeing the independence of the individual within the Ecosystem and the creation of a critical and conscious community."</p>
    
    <div class="stacco"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #FFF;">"The Global Trend Forum® is a totally independent space, free from any external bias. We protect freedom of expression and the central role of the individual."</p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h4>05 — SUPPORT THE AUTHENTICITY OF THE HUMAN</h4>
    <h1 style="font-size: 38px;">The Value of Authenticity: Fund Human Evolution</h1>

    <p><strong>The Citizens of the World — From the strategic convergence between the vanguards of the G7, the frontier of the BRICS Countries, and the Far East, to global mobilization:</strong> When humanity unites, technology goes back to being a tool for amplifying talent. Support the Think Tank with a free contribution (€5, €20, €50). The support of thousands of citizens ensures that research, culture, and tomorrow's source code remain pure, ethical, and oriented toward the expression of true individuality.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 20px; margin-top: 30px;">FUND THE DEVELOPMENT OF THE FIRST ETHICAL FRAMEWORK AND CITY MODEL FOR THE HUMANIZATION AND DEMOCRATIZATION OF AI</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--neon-cyan);"><em>(57% Achieved | 1,287 Supporters | 142.5k Euro Raised | Target: €250,000 / month)</em></p>

    <!-- FORM SECTION -->
    <div style="background: var(--card-bg); border: 2px solid var(--neon-cyan); padding: 35px; margin-bottom: 40px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);">
        <h2 style="margin-top:0; border-left: 4px solid var(--neon-green); padding-left: 15px; font-size: 30px; color: #FFF;" id="form-delibera">RECLAIM YOUR TIME: SIGN AND JOIN THE MOVEMENT</h2>
        <p style="color:#A1A1AA; font-size:16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">Make your mark to change the rules. Your vote carries fundamental political weight.</p>
        
        <form id="form-delibera-actual" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;">
            <label style="font-weight:bold; color: #FFF;">Full Name:</label>
            <input type="text" name="NomeCognome" required style="padding: 12px; background: #16161A; border: 1px solid #27272A; color: #FFF; border-radius: 6px;">
            
            <label style="font-weight:bold; color: #FFF;">Email Address:</label>
            <input type="email" name="Email" required style="padding: 12px; background: #16161A; border: 1px solid #27272A; color: #FFF; border-radius: 6px;">
            
            <label style="font-weight:bold; color: #FFF;">Select your region / area:</label>
            <select name="Area" required style="padding: 12px; background: #16161A; border: 1px solid #27272A; color: #FFF; border-radius: 6px;">
                <option value="Salerno">🔴 Salerno and Province (Local priority)</option>
                <option value="Campania">🟢 Other Provinces of Campania (Regional support)</option>
                <option value="Italia">🇮🇹 Other Regions of Italy (National support)</option>
                <option value="Estero">🌍 International / Abroad (International Endorsement)</option>
            </select>
            
            <label style="font-weight:bold; color: #FFF;">Specific City or Foreign Country:</label>
            <input type="text" name
